rawIntent:
[Feature: Build the leave management module — Phase 1: LeaveRequest and AuditRecord domain models with persistence]

Create approximately 5 files: src/modules/leave/leave.model.ts, src/modules/leave/leave.repository.ts, src/modules/audit/audit.model.ts, src/modules/audit/audit.repository.ts, and tests/unit/modules/leave/leave.repository.test.ts. Define the canonical LeaveRequest (id, employeeId, leaveType, status) and AuditRecord (id, entityType, entityId, action) types plus DTOs needed by the repositories. Implement repository interfaces and PostgreSQL-backed repository implementations. Add createLeaveRequest() persistence behavior that stores a LeaveRequest in PENDING status and writes an AuditRecord. Include unit tests covering repository behavior.

Phase architecture notes:
Establish repository-pattern boundaries for leave and audit modules; keep models and repositories in the same phase.

